							
							⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ DOM MANIPULATION IN REACT : ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

👉️👉️👉️ Get all the Input elements on formSubmit:

	[ e: SyntheticEvent<HTMLFormElement> ]
	const form = e.target as HTMLFormElement; // returns the Form element in "html format" 
	const inputs = form.querySelectorAll("input"); // returns an array of all the Input childrens
	
👉️👉️👉️ get the current element

	e.currentTarget; // is the element where the event is being performed.
